trans-unit.source: Defines events for a class.
trans-unit.target: Definiuje zdarzenia dla klasy.

trans-unit.source: An `EventBuilder` is always associated with a `TypeBuilder`.
trans-unit.target: `EventBuilder` Zawsze jest skojarzony z `TypeBuilder`.

trans-unit.source: The TypeBuilder.DefineEvent method will return a new `EventBuilder` to a client.
trans-unit.target: Metoda TypeBuilder.DefineEvent zwróci nowy `EventBuilder` do klienta.

trans-unit.source: A <see langword="MethodBuilder" /> object that represents the other method.
trans-unit.target: A <see langword="MethodBuilder" /> obiekt, który reprezentuje innej metody.

trans-unit.source: Adds one of the "other" methods associated with this event.
trans-unit.target: Dodaje jednej z metod "other" skojarzonego z tym zdarzeniem.

trans-unit.source: "Other" methods are methods other than the "on" and "raise" methods associated with an event.
trans-unit.target: "Other" metody to metody inne niż "na" i "podnieść" metody skojarzone ze zdarzeniem.

trans-unit.source: This function can be called many times to add as many "other" methods.
trans-unit.target: Ta funkcja może zostać wywołana wiele razy można dodać dowolną liczbę metod "other".

trans-unit.target: <paramref name="mdBuilder" /> jest <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: Returns the token for this event.
